Verb Method Step.

This recipe tests the "verb" method step. Verb can be one of a number of
possible supported verbs.

Ingredients.
100 g flour
500 g butter
3 onions

Method.
Sift the flour.
Rub the butter.
Rub the butter until rubbed.
Sift the flour until sifted.
Heat the butter.
Melt the butter until heated.
Melt the butter.
Cook the onions.
Caramelise the onions.
Cook the onions until caramelised.
Caramelise the onions until cooked.
Heat the butter until melted.
Cook the onions.
Heat until cooked.

Serves 1.
